%F A002838 a(n) = A047997(n, n) = A067059(n, n+1). a(n) tends towards (sqrt(12)/Pi)*4^n/n^2 and something like (sqrt(12)/Pi)*4^n/(n^2+1.85*n+0.8) seems to give an even closer approximation. - _Henry Bottomley_, Aug 09 2002
